for verb in [self.app.get, self.app.post, self.app.put, self.app.patch,
    self.app.delete]:
    response = verb('/%s/movies' % self.api)
    self.assertEqual(response.status_code, 401)
    response_json = json.loads(response.data or '{}')
    self.assertDictEqual(response_json, {'message': 
        u'You must be logged in "%s" api' % self.api})
